summary: An Ordinance providing for the purchase of portions of Lot Three (3), Block Forty-two (42); Lots Three (3), Four (4), Ten (10) and Eleven (11), Block Forty-five (45); Lots nine (9), Ten (10) and Eleven (11), Block Fifty-four (54); and portions of Unplatted Block Fifty-one (51), Yesler's Third Addition to the City of Seattle, for park and parkway purposes, for a sum not to exceed Eight Thousand Seven Hundred Sixty and fifty one-hundredths Dollars (8760.50).
